alerts.description: Bei positiven Temperaturen und andauerndem Regen tritt ein starkes Abtauen der Schneedecke ein. Die Abflussmengen erreichen bis 40 l/m².

There is a risk of thaw (Level 2 of 3).
Runoff: < 40 l/m²

There is a risk of violent storm gusts (Level 3 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 90-110 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 120 km/h

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: 50-60 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 70 km/h
Es treten oberhalb 600 m schwere Sturmböen mit Geschwindigkeiten zwischen 75 km/h (21m/s, 41kn, Bft 9) und 90 km/h (25m/s, 48kn, Bft 10) aus südwestlicher Richtung auf.

There is a risk of storm-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 600 m; Max. gusts: 75-90 km/h; Wind direction: south-west
